name: TEA TOWEL — Almond deep olive
description:
100% Cotton white quality tea towel 
with design, woven to last from one 
of England’s oldest established textile 
manufacturing company. 

Tea towel size 50cm x 76cm with loop 
on the side for hanging.

Screen printed using specialist eco-friendly 
inks 100% solvent free and chemical free inks.

Machine wash 30c and Hand wash 
recommended as it will extend the 
life colour.

All items are hand printed so some 
variation will occur.
